    <p class="section-sub sr sr-delay-2" style="margin-bottom:40px;">根据用户访问量实时统计，以下是本周最受欢迎的计算工具。</p>

    <div class="featured-grid sr sr-delay-2">
      <div class="featured-main" role="article">
        <div>
          <div class="tag-chip" style="margin-bottom:12px;">🏆 本周 #1</div>
          <h3 class="featured-main-title">留学总费用计算器</h3>
