        </a>
        <a href="https://geshui.jisuan.help" class="featured-item">
          <div class="featured-item-icon fi-purple">📋</div>
          <div class="featured-item-body">
            <div class="featured-item-title">个人所得税计算</div>
            <div class="featured-item-meta">月薪 → 实际到手</div>
          </div>
          <div class="featured-item-stat">本周 7,350 次</div>
        </a>
        <a href="https://yuegong.jisuan.help" class="featured-item">
          <div class="featured-item-icon fi-blue">🏠</div>
          <div class="featured-item-body">
            <div class="featured-item-title">贷款月供计算</div>
