        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ WHY US ═══ -->
<section id="why" class="section" aria-labelledby="why-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:48px;">
      <div class="section-eyebrow sr" aria-hidden="true">平台优势</div>
      <h2 class="section-title sr sr-delay-1" id="why-heading">为什么选 jisuan.help</h2>
      <p class="section-sub sr sr-delay-2" style="margin:0 auto;">免费、精准、即用，专为华人留学生和新移民设计的计算工具平台。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-grid">
      <div class="why-card sr sr-delay-1">
        <div class="why-icon">⚡</div>
        <h3 class="why-title">秒出结果</h3>
        <p class="why-desc">浏览器端直接计算，无需等待，结果即填即出，不依赖服务器响应。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card sr sr-delay-2">
        <div class="why-icon">🎯</div>
        <h3 class="why-title">数据精准</h3>
        <p class="why-desc">学费 / 签证费 / 汇率参数每周由编辑团队核对官方数据，不用过期来源。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card sr sr-delay-3">
        <div class="why-icon">🔒</div>
        <h3 class="why-title">零隐私风险</h3>
        <p class="why-desc">无需注册、无需填写手机邮箱，计算数据不上传服务器，纯本地运算。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card sr sr-delay-4">
        <div class="why-icon">📱</div>
        <h3 class="why-title">全平台可用</h3>
        <p class="why-desc">桌面端/手机端完美自适应，随时随地在手机上算完发给家长或朋友。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ INLINE DEMO CALCULATOR ═══ -->
<section id="demo" class="section" aria-labelledby="demo-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="demo-wrapper">
      <div class="demo-copy sr">
        <div class="section-eyebrow" aria-hidden="true">在线试算</div>
        <h2 class="section-title" id="demo-heading">贷款月供，现在就算</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">
          无需跳转，在这里直接试算房贷或个人贷款月供。
          等额本息 / 等额本金两种方式，结果即时呈现。
        </p>
        <div class="demo-features" style="margin-top:24px;">
          <div class="demo-feat">
            <div class="demo-feat-icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</div>
            公开金融公式，与银行官方计算器一致
          </div>
          <div class="demo-feat">
            <div class="demo-feat-icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</div>
            支持 AUD / CNY / GBP / USD 贷款
          </div>
          <div class="demo-feat">
            <div class="demo-feat-icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</div>
            自动拆分本金/利息明细，一目了然
          </div>
          <div class="demo-feat">
            <div class="demo-feat-icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</div>
            仅供参考，实际贷款请咨询持牌贷款顾问
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="calc-widget sr sr-delay-2" role="form" aria-label="贷款月供计算器">
        <div class="calc-widget-header">
          <div class="calc-widget-dots">
            <div class="calc-widget-dot dot-r"></div>
            <div class="calc-widget-dot dot-y"></div>
            <div class="calc-widget-dot dot-g"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="calc-widget-title">🏠 贷款月供计算器 — yuegong.jisuan.help</div>
        </div>
        <div class="calc-widget-body">
          <div class="cw-tabs" role="tablist">
            <button class="cw-tab active" role="tab" aria-selected="true" onclick="setCwTab('annuity', this)">等额本息</button>
            <button class="cw-tab" role="tab" aria-selected="false" onclick="setCwTab('principal', this)">等额本金</button>
            <button class="cw-tab" role="tab" aria-selected="false" onclick="setCwTab('interest', this)">利息总额</button>
          </div>

          <div class="cw-field">
            <label class="cw-label" for="cw-principal">贷款金额（元）</label>
            <input class="cw-input" type="number" id="cw-principal" placeholder="如 1000000" min="1000" step="1000">
          </div>
          <div class="cw-row">
            <div class="cw-field">
              <label class="cw-label" for="cw-rate">年利率 (%)</label>
              <input class="cw-input" type="number" id="cw-rate" placeholder="如 4.3" step="0.01" min="0.1">
            </div>
            <div class="cw-field">
              <label class="cw-label" for="cw-months">还款月数</label>
              <input class="cw-input" type="number" id="cw-months" placeholder="如 360" min="1" max="480">
            </div>
          </div>

          <button class="cw-calc-btn" onclick="calcLoan()" aria-label="计算月供">计算月供</button>

          <div class="cw-result" id="cw-result" role="region" aria-live="polite" aria-label="计算结果">
            <div class="cw-result-label">每月还款金额</div>
            <div class="cw-result-amount" id="cw-monthly">—</div>
            <div class="cw-result-breakdown" id="cw-breakdown"></div>
            <div class="cw-disclaimer">仅供参考 · 实际还款金额以银行最终核定为准</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ FAQ ═══ -->
<section id="faq" class="section" aria-labelledby="faq-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:44px;">
      <div class="section-eyebrow sr" aria-hidden="true">常见问题</div>
      <h2 class="section-title sr sr-delay-1" id="faq-heading">高频问题快答</h2>
    </div>
